RAMA Change Log File

-For new changeLogs, have a look at the svn log

-09/22/2005 
Added a verbose option to display the number of iterations. 

-09/06/2005
Removed C++ style comments

-09/01/2005
Added an option to compute log ratio credible intervals

-09/01/2005
Changed the default number of iteration in fit.model

-06/20/2005
Set rho=0 in the estimation of the shift function. A value of rho
different from zero could lead (in a few cases) to an extremely large
estimated shift.
